&lt;p&gt;Pamela Crawford, Chief Pharmacy Technician – Ward Service Manager, Telephone number: 0115 969 1169 Ext: 65780 (QMC), Email: pamela.crawford@nuh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
